==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[transmigratio]]''.

===Noun===
'''transmigration'''

# [[departure|Departure]] from one's [[homeland]] to live in another [[country]]; [[migration]].
# The movement of a [[soul]] from one [[body]] to another after [[death]]; [[metempsychosis]].

